0:startevent:((startevent)) --> 1:task:(Search for Customer)
1:task:(Search for Customer) --> 2:task:(Make Offer)
2:task:(Make Offer) --> 3:exclusivegateway:{x}

%% First decision: continue or skip to next decision
3:exclusivegateway:{x} --> |Continue|4:task:(Receive Additional Request)
3:exclusivegateway:{x} --> |Do not continue|6:exclusivegateway:{x}

4:task:(Receive Additional Request) --> 5:task:(Provide More Details)
