6:exclusivegateway:{x} --> |Continue|7:task:(Receive Booking Request)
6:exclusivegateway:{x} --> |Do not continue|9:exclusivegateway:{x}

7:task:(Receive Booking Request) --> 8:task:(Send Bill)
8:task:(Send Bill) --> 9:exclusivegateway:{x}

%% Third decision: continue or skip to next decision
9:exclusivegateway:{x} --> |Continue|10:task:(Receive Payment)
9:exclusivegateway:{x} --> |Do not continue|11:exclusivegateway:{x}

10:task:(Receive Payment) --> 11:exclusivegateway:{x}

%% Fourth decision: continue or go to final decision
11:exclusivegateway:{x} --> |Continue|12:exclusivegateway:{x}
11:exclusivegateway:{x} --> |Do not continue|12:exclusivegateway:{x}

%% Final decision: continue to booking or contact customer and loop back
